[Course_Description]
When you have a job that you really love—where you feel valued and have room to grow—chances are, you have a great manager. In this course from management and leadership expert Dr. Eric Zackrison, learn how to become a manager that your team loves. Dr. Zackrison shows how to create and establish strong relationships with the people on your team, and how to move from a manager to a leader. He also discusses sources of power and leadership, how to set yourself up for success, and the key skills of great supervisors. This course was created by Madecraft. We are pleased to host this training in our library.